This is an EXPERIMENTAL version for evaluation purposes only. See
the RELEASE_NOTES file for more information.

Compiling & Installing under Linux/Unix
---------------------------------------

	 $ ./config.sh
	 $ make
	 # make install

Installing the Win32 version
----------------------------

Create a directory called C:\Program Files\mp-5 (or however your
localized Program Files directory is called in your Windows version)
and copy all *.mpsl files and the wmp.exe executable there.

